data.description: ** Mortgage Lender offering $3,000.00 incentive**Check out this beautiful home! This home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with an open floor plan. This home also features  Wood flooring in living area, 3 CM full flab granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms. Stainless steel appliances, tankless hot water heater, double vanity & walk -in closet in master bath. This home was very well taken care of. Freash paint on all interior walls. A covered back porch to lounge and enjoy some peaceful afternoons! WAIT!! There is more, A concrete slab already laied for your very own basketball court, and or it can be used for your preference!  Schedule your showing today! You don't want to miss out!
